data.title: Today's top celebrity birthdays list for January 17, 2019
data.meta_description: Celebrities Zooey Deschanel, James Earl Jones and Jim Carrey share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of famous people with birthdays on January 17, 2019 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Associated Press

Top celebrity birthdays on January 17, 2019

Birthday wishes go out to Zooey Deschanel, James Earl Jones, Jim Carrey and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on January 17th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

-Mike Rose, cleveland.com

Associated Press

Actress Betty White turns 97

Fun facts: Turned down the role of Helen Hunt's mother in 'As Good As It Gets'

Associated Press

Betty White fun facts

Check out 16 interesting things you might not know about actress Betty White.

Associated Press

Actor James Earl Jones turns 88

Fun facts: Jones first film credit was in 'Dr. Strangelove'

Getty Images

TV host Maury Povich turns 80

Fun facts: Has appeared as himself in 'Wings,' '30 Rock' and 'How I Met Your Mother'

Associated Press

Comedian Steve Harvey turns 62

Fun facts: Born in West Virginia but grew up in Cleveland, Ohio

Associated Press

Musician Susanna Hoffs turns 60

Fun facts: The Bangles star was also part of Mike Myers band Ming Tea

Associated Press

Actor Jim Carrey turns 57

Fun facts: Carrey became a U.S. citizen in 2004

Associated Press

Former first lady Michelle Obama turns 55

Fun facts: Her older brother used to coach basketball at Brown University and Oregon State

Associated Press

Actor Joshua Malina turns 53

Fun facts: Malina is married to costumer Melissa Merwin

Associated Press

Rapper Kid Rock turns 48

Fun facts: Full name is Robert James Ritchie

Associated Press

Actress Zooey Deschanel turns 39

Fun facts: Zooey's first film appearance was in 'Mumford'

Associated Press

Actress Kelly Marie Tran turns 30

Fun facts: Tran once worked at a yogurt shop to earn money for acting headshots

Getty Images

Actress Kathrine Herzer turns 22

Fun facts: Is the daughter of media mogul Sumner Redstone

More celebrities with birthdays today

Pop singer Chris Montez is 77. Rhythm-and-blues singer William Hart (The Delfonics) is 74. Actress Joanna David is 72. Actress Jane Elliot is 72. Rock musician Mick Taylor is 71. Rhythm-and-blues singer Sheila Hutchinson (The Emotions) is 66. Singer Steve Earle is 64. Singer Paul Young is 63. Movie director-screenwriter Brian Helgeland is 58. Actor Denis O'Hare is 57. Singer Shabba Ranks is 53. Rock musician Jon Wysocki is 51. Actor Naveen Andrews is 50. Electronic music DJ Tiesto is 50. Actor Freddy Rodriguez is 44. Actor-writer Leigh Whannel is 42. Dancer Maksim Chmerkovskiy (TV: "Dancing with the Stars") is 39. Singer Ray J is 38. Actor Diogo Morgado is 38. Country singer Amanda Wilkinson is 37. NBA player Dwyane Wade is 37. Actor Ryan Gage is 36. DJ-singer Calvin Harris is 35. Folk-rock musician Jeremiah Fraites is 33. Actor Jonathan Keltz is 31.
